#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/3.2/guides/resteasy-reactive.adoc:2575
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"    @Override\n"
"    public Converter fromString(String value) {\n"
"        return new Converter(value);\n"
"    }\n"
